{"tid":180150,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考私家車棍仔既我係咪好傻?","createTime":"2017-03-30T17:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T10:50:21.000Z","uid":54188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2505994bb70bf16a1ea9dbee8f1b191ea75e802e","tid":180150,"uid":54188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"想問下P牌期間可唔可以考埋棍波van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb43eab831855a817170548351fdf22e2903f793","tid":180150,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下P牌期間可唔可以考埋棍波van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以<br />\n但唔係必要揸棍van就唔好去考<br />\n又要錢又要時間<br />\n印象中好似某類型車  可以送番個棍波牌俾你<br />\n等其他巴打答"},{"pid":"7ad0e8163b981aa5818fd4f139888f082662086e","tid":180150,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c988280b74b91ff3391bc78adc63c5a2e2fdb39e","tid":180150,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下P牌期間可唔可以考埋棍波van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以<br />\n但唔係必要揸棍van就唔好去考<br />\n又要錢又要時間<br />\n印象中好似某類型車  可以送番個貨van牌俾你<br />\n等其他巴打答</blockquote><br />\n18 \t中型貨車 \t此乃商用車輛執照。貨車指總重量超過5.5公噸但不超過24公噸的貨車。未持有輕型貨車執照（2號牌）者，成功考取中型貨車執照後免試加簽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B%E5%9F%B7%E7%85%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A7%2595%25E9%25A7%259B%25E5%259F%25B7%25E7%2585%25A7&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b217241a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B%E5%9F%B7%E7%85%A7</a>"},{"pid":"9a623e0d3e0385d6800b828ef8438374f56ffdd3","tid":180150,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d87c73ba26c967095eeeed284846d4f007a65505","tid":180150,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係幾傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過考到就好勁，棍私最難考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起步仲難過棍van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950f552c0d13094f0b9f9dfec5ed327f3ace36d3","tid":180150,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下P牌期間可唔可以考埋棍波van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n棍私齋吊極力子仲要比啲油先起到步，棍van齋吊都已經識行。棍van扭力大啲冇咁易死火。如果講易考一定係棍van"},{"pid":"fa61357319538914a1b0bc6cad06305ebc4cee7e","tid":180150,"uid":126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下P牌期間可唔可以考埋棍波van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n棍私齋吊極力子仲要比啲油先起到步，棍van齋吊都已經識行。棍van扭力大啲冇咁易死火。如果講易考一定係棍van</blockquote><br />\n仲有van 仔無頭同坐高左，睇位易得多"},{"pid":"fbee8e0f56ffd75d1cd676a4e2fe0796d7b5be1e","tid":180150,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下P牌期間可唔可以考埋棍波van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n棍私齋吊極力子仲要比啲油先起到步，棍van齋吊都已經識行。棍van扭力大啲冇咁易死火。如果講易考一定係棍van</blockquote><br />\n仲有van 仔無頭同坐高左，睇位易得多</blockquote><br />\n同埋可以睇少車尾盲點，車尾玻璃變左塊板"},{"pid":"5c6ddb9a08b1a3e96ee7965c10d20d0f2d9f6e80","tid":180150,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"想知樓主幾多take pass<br />\n其實幾勁"},{"pid":"9be22d36e618b64ddfdb718f81e0019e24a1d05a","tid":180150,"uid":54188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep